TABLE.NAME: osa
TABLE.COMMENT: Stores the osa activity module instances.

FIELD.NAME: course
FIELD.COMMENT: ID of the course this activity is part of.

FIELD.NAME: name
FIELD.COMMENT: The name of the activity module instance

FIELD.NAME: timecreated
FIELD.COMMENT: Timestamp of when the instance was added to the course.

FIELD.NAME: timemodified
FIELD.COMMENT: Timestamp of when the instance was last modified.

FIELD.NAME: introformat
FIELD.COMMENT: The format of the intro field.

FIELD.NAME: osasettingtextoptional
FIELD.COMMENT: Teacher mode create osa text optional

FIELD.NAME: osasettingtextoptionalformat
FIELD.COMMENT: Teacher mode create osa text optional format

FIELD.NAME: osasettingimageoptional
FIELD.COMMENT: Teacher mode create osa image optional

FIELD.NAME: osasettingimageoptionalformat
FIELD.COMMENT: Teacher mode create osa image optional format

FIELD.NAME: nextcompletionindays
FIELD.COMMENT: next completion is allowed in x days
